Class QuadraticProbingHashTable<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.icafe4j.util.QuadraticProbingHashTable<K,V>

  • public class QuadraticProbingHashTable<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    Quadratic probing hash table.
    Version:
    1.0 06/03/2007 Based on QuadraticProbingHashTable.java

    Probing table implementation of hash tables. Note that all "matching" is based on the equals method.

    Author:
    Wen Yu, yuwen_66@yahoo.com, Mark Allen Weiss
